🎨 AI Color Palette Generator

This project is an AI-based color palette generator built using Gradio and Python.

---

🌟 Features

- Upload an image and extract its dominant colors
- Displays a palette preview with color codes and names
- Easy-to-use web interface powered by Gradio

---

🚀 How it works

- Uses K-Means clustering to find the most prominent colors in an image
- Converts colors to HEX codes and approximate color names
- Generates a palette image to visualize the colors

